      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required for MRL 2 at this factor level; scoping decision documented.",
      "rationale": "Simulation setup was performed by experienced CFD analysts following a documented simulation plan. Formal use-error analysis is not required at MRL 2 and was scoped out based on analyst qualification records."
