      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required for MRL 2 at this factor level; scoping decision documented.",
      "rationale": "Experimental data from the FDA inter-laboratory study provide sufficient sample coverage for MRL 2 comparison purposes. Statistical characterization of test sample variability is not required at this risk level."
    },
    {
