    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors achieved levels meeting or exceeding the required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors were appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 guidance for MRL 2. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device within the scope of this assessment.",
